{"type": "article", "id": 5584, "title": "Lumo Lift 矫正器", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-27T07:42:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234028UPnJ1cOlRaqLeFYS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t不知是否还有人记得，曾经一款名叫背背佳的矫形产品风靡一时。现在，有人打算用更温和的方式来做这件事。Lumo Lift 是一个小型的矫正器，全身大小就是一块小小的方形薄片装置，利用磁铁的方式别在用户身上，装置的感应机制可以自动监测。不管是坐着还是站着，之邀用户出现弯腰驼背的情况，Lumo Lift 就会发出提醒要求用户端正姿势。此外，Lumo Lift 还搭配有相应手机应用，坚持用户的日常体能状况，包括站立、走路或者跑步等数据。定价 99.99 美元（约合人民币 625 元），<a href=\"https://liftstore.lumobodytech.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234025CrQ03IepS5G41mfA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234026jDziuXKrEblsoBCP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71329879\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234026rDSYt9zXQCcaj02W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234027sgbJWRvzlmxfN9Sq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}